text: Abnecotants Island is a very small island in the middle of Squam Swamp in northeastern portion of the island of Nantucket in Massachusetts. ==External links== ==References== *http://www.topozone.com/map.asp?lon=-70.0011255⪫=41.313177&datum;=nad83 Category:Coastal islands of Massachusetts Category:Islands of Nantucket County, Massachusetts
